SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4223
A bill to amend 1976 PA 451, entitled
"The revised school code,"
(MCL 380.1 to 380.1852) by adding section 1308g.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 1308g. Beginning with the 2026-2027 school year, the
2 governing body of a public school or nonpublic school shall develop
3 or adopt, and implement, a school safety and security training plan
4 as described in section 1308f, and shall ensure that school
5 resource officers placed in the public school or nonpublic school,
6 school safety or security personnel who work at or for the public
7 school or nonpublic school, members of a crisis response team
8 described in section 1308b, and all school staff of the public
9 school or nonpublic school complete the training described in
CRM H00075'25 (H-1) kch07p

2
1 section 1308f, as applicable.
2 Enacting section 1. This amendatory act does not take effect
3 unless all of the following bills of the 103rd Legislature are
4 enacted into law.
5 (a) House Bill No. 4222.
6 (b) House Bill No. 4315.
